{"tid":585982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曾被控性侵　1萬7千網友連署撤消Kobe奧斯卡獎","createTime":"2018-03-09T07:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T17:30:52.000Z","uid":90,"like":18,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"93cfc92296c22d8ee36fd71018efbd6ce374428c","tid":585982,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"NBA傳奇球星Kobe(Kobe Bryant)，本周一才風光拿到奧斯卡金像獎的「最佳動畫短片」，<a href=\"http://但據美媒clutchpoints.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%86%E6%93%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%AA%92clutchpoints.com&d=r0zjJVD0uMBiPm%2BTbH9UJU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=eb9c8c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">但據美媒clutchpoints.com</a>報導，有超過1萬7千人在網路上連署，希望奧斯卡獎能撤消Kobe的獎項，理由是：「奧斯卡幾乎做到了不把獎項頒給性侵者，Kobe也不應該例外。」<br />\n<br />\nKobe在2003年曾被控在丹佛性侵一名飯店女服務生，最後雙方達成和解，女方才同意撤告，但這件事已成Kobe職業生涯最大的汙點。<br />\n<br />\n在連署撤消Kobe奧斯卡獎的網站上寫著，奧斯卡幾乎做到了不把獎項頒給性侵者，像大導演伍迪艾倫(Woody Allen)和知名演員詹姆士法蘭柯(James Franco)都沒有得到奧斯卡，而Kobe做為一個被指控性侵的人，卻得到了奧斯卡。"},{"pid":"b840ab8016255f09e829fdd237c98aa2e84010b2","tid":585982,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難得正式超越mj"},{"pid":"6c4f6a866932cb818e225c0588bb163b2825db95","tid":585982,"uid":19126,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:06:12.000Z","msg":"女人又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#mewin <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1cb702189441b021adb4db5391defd04f17de7","tid":585982,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.